wnby-geolocation-geoip-fallback:
This is an informatory message. The external link to the Wikipedia article included in this message may be adapted if your language provides such an article.

The parameters used:
* $1 - Holds the latitude value of the coordinate
* $2 - Holds the longitude value of the coordinates
wnby-geolocation-geoip-no-fallback:
This is an error message.

The parameters used:
* $1 - Holds the latitude value of the coordinate
* $2 - Holds the longitude value of the coordinates
wnby-no-fallback-location:
This is an informatory message.

Fallback = Location shown when no geoposition was detected.
wnby-default-fallback-location:
This is an informatory message.

Fallback = Location shown when no geoposition was detected.
